---
title: Garlic-Herb Beef Rump & Veggie Fries with Radish Salad
description: Bold, herby, and downright delicious, this beef rump is a flavour-packed feast! Juicy, perfectly cooked beef gets a punchy kick from our garlic & herb seasoning, while crispy veggie fries bring the crunch. A fresh, peppery radish salad ties it all together for a  dish that’s as colourful as it is crave-worthy. Get ready to impress your taste buds!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
